# denotes [[duration]] of an [[action]], e.g. '''[[danci]]''' ''to [[dance]]'', '''dancado''' ''dancing''.
# with verbs derived from [[nominal]] [[root]]s, can denote the simple action of the verb without connotation of duration, e.g. '''[[krono]]''' ''[[crown]] (noun)'', '''[[kroni]]''' ''to [[crown]]'', '''[[kronado]]''' ''a coronation''.

